      "content": "idk, i dont know if they have bonds anymore. it feels like they're just constant pain, honestly. like every second they exist, they're just losing more of themselves. part of me feels like the character is just better off if they just give in. if they just stop and embrace the nothingness, wouldn't that be more of a relief than fighting a losing battle?",
